title: Nine Inch Nails: The Definitive NIN - Quiet Tracks (2006)
description:
The Definitive Nine Inch Nails: Quiet Tracks

A compilation album featuring 19 of NIN&#039;s quieter songs and instrumentals.  A good way to get acquainted with a side of the band many people are unfamiliar with.  This is the third release in a three-piece "Best Of" collection.

This torrent includes high-res artwork and an html file with information about NIN and this release.  All files are MP3 192kbps and include artwork and lyrics.
